<p>FREE ADMISSION!!!<br /> Saturday, March 23<sup>rd</sup> 6-9 pm</p>
<h4>Join us at the BYU-Idaho Outdoor Learning Center for a <strong>fun family sled night</strong>! <br /><br /> We have <span style="text-decoration: underline;">sleds available</span> for your use, and no need to walk up the hill, just use the tow-rope!<br /> Also, a large canvas tent will be nearby for you and your family to warm up and recharge for another go at the sled hill! <br /><br /> Reserve your spot <a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_dg3dW5NdjfgVHfL">here</a>!<br /> &nbsp;<br /><br /> All families using the sled hill must sign a waiver. You can print the waiver from the link below.<br /> <a href="http://www.byui.edu/Documents/badger-creek/Liability_Waiver.pdf">http://www.byui.edu/Documents/badger-creek/Liability_Waiver.pdf</a><br /><br /> &nbsp;<br /><br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sled Hill Rules</span><br /> 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No jumps<br /> 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It is the participant's responsibility to avoid other people and objects on the sled hill.<br /> 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not attach a sled rope to the rope tow. Younger participants who can't hold on to the tow rope must&nbsp;&nbsp; be accompanied by an adult.<br /> 4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All children under the age of 12 must be supervised by an adult.<br /> 5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Each group is responsible to return the sleds to the tow shack.<br /> 6. All participants must fill out and sign a liability waiver. Participants under 18 must have a waiver signed by their parent or legal guardian.</h4>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="Semesters" label="Available Semesters" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><AvailableFall type="boolean" label="Available Fall" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</AvailableFall><AvailableWinter type="boolean" label="Available Winter" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</AvailableWinter><Ava